@NODE wids "What's DirScanner ???"

 @{B}What's DirScanner ???@{UB}

 DirScanner were developed because of personal needings
 (like all good programs:-)). There was a time (let's say
 two months ago:-)) when I had no CD-ROM and all search-
 programs I found, were really sucking because they were not
 fontsensitive and I HATE topaz/8!!! Therefore I decided to
 write my own search program but I had not the Developer-CD
 thus I wrote it using MUI, sorry to everyone I know that MUI
 isn't THE solution but it is very easy to implement it and it
 is @{B}fontsensitive@{UB}!!! And so began my adventure
 DirScanner, one of my first (released) programs. Anyway do
 I think that it's not too bad but if you have any suggestions:
 write @{"me" LINK autor}!

 But now: have fun!

@ENDNODE wids

